  "text": "For the aforementioned reasons, a systematic approach is needed to identify the stress-response targets and metabolic pathways involved when reacting to DON exposure [CITATION_1] . The more we know about the nature of such protein-targets and enzymes, the better our grasp of how cells handle DON-related toxicities will be.",
